Invocation Name: american hundred cities
des:
You can check the location of major cities in the United States. 
A screen-attached device is required to use this skill.

How to invocate: Alexa, open american hundred cities
Say a city name (example): New York, Boston
Say next: next, next city
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
